## Workflow

This project uses beads (`bd`) for issue tracking and Ralph automation loops for implementation.

### Creating a Feature

1. **Capture your idea**:
   ```bash
   ./idea.sh "Your feature idea"
   ```

2. **Run the interactive interview**:
   ```bash
   ./interview.sh
   ```
   Claude will ask clarifying questions, generate a PRD, and create implementation tasks.

3. **Implement tasks with Ralph**:
   ```bash
   ./ralph.sh
   ```
   Ralph picks up tasks and implements them one by one.

### Issue Tracking Commands

```bash
bd list              # List all issues
bd ready             # Show issues ready to work
bd show <id>         # View issue details
bd stats             # Project statistics
```

